    <text><body>
            <div type="writingSession">
                <pb n="1r"/>
                <opener>
                    <dateline><orgName ref="https://edition-humboldt.de/H0000559 http://d-nb.info/gnd/1018641-4"><choice>
                                <abbr>Rl</abbr>
                                <expan>Royal</expan>
                            </choice> Gardens</orgName>
                        <placeName ref="https://edition-humboldt.de/H0000407 https://www.geonames.org/2645740">Kew</placeName> August 7<hi rendition="#sup"><hi rendition="#u">th</hi></hi> 1857</dateline>
                    <salute>My dear Baron Humboldt</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>The bearer of this, Mr <lb/><persName ref="https://edition-humboldt.de/H8894976">Polyblank</persName> of
                        <placeName ref="https://edition-humboldt.de/H0011492 https://www.geonames.org/2643743">London</placeName>, has <lb/>rendered Science a
                    very <lb/>great service, by the series <lb/>of unrivalled portraits of
                    <lb/>Scientific men which he <lb/>has executed in Photograph, <lb/>&amp;
                    supplied to the members <lb/>of the <orgName ref="https://edition-humboldt.de/H0000583 http://d-nb.info/gnd/39272-8">Royal</orgName>
                    &amp; <orgName ref="https://edition-humboldt.de/H6654236 https://d-nb.info/gnd/38819-1">Linnaean <lb/>Societies</orgName> at the smallest
                    <lb/>possible cost.</p>
                <p>Mr <persName ref="https://edition-humboldt.de/H8894976">Polyblank</persName> hopes for <pb n="1v"/><add place="superlinear">the</add> privilege of obtaining a <lb/>Sitting from
                    you, &amp; I need <lb/>not say that if you feel <lb/>able to grant him this
                    <lb/>honor, you will afford <lb/>the highest gratification <lb/>to hosts in this
                        <placeName ref="https://edition-humboldt.de/H0010934 https://www.geonames.org/2635167">country</placeName>. <lb/>I can with confidence
                    assert, <lb/>that there is no artist <lb/>from whom we would <lb/>rather have
                    such a portrait <lb/>than Mr <persName ref="https://edition-humboldt.de/H8894976">Polyblank</persName>.</p>
                <closer>
                    <salute>Ever Your affectionate &amp; devoted</salute>
                    <signed><persName ref="https://edition-humboldt.de/H0011992 http://d-nb.info/gnd/118774891">J. D<supplied cert="high">.</supplied> Hooker</persName></signed>.</closer>
            </div>
